videos.headline: Akron QB drops dime TD
videos.description: Akron quarterback Kato Nelson drops a perfect pass to wide receiver Kwadarrius Smith for a 35-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Akron RB carves up defense for 21-yard TD
videos.description: Akron running back Van Edwards Jr. maneuvers tacklers to cruise in for a 21-yard rushing touchdown.

videos.headline: Zips QB tosses dart for 32-yard TD
videos.description: Akron quarterback Kato Nelson connects with wide receiver Andre Williams for a 32-yard touchdown before halftime.

videos.headline: Akron RB tiptoes in for 20-yard TD
videos.description: Akron running back Van Edwards Jr. bursts to the sideline and tiptoes into the end zone for a 20-yard touchdown, his second of the game.
